This is the NEWS file for the 'flipscript' package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.7.1 - 23 May 2025

Changes:
   Scripit Sorting. Modified the flip(1) and mscp(1) '--list' command to sort
   the output.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.7.0 - 23 May 2025

Changes:
   Batched File Copying. Added a mscp(1) to allow file copying to multiple
   remote hosts via scp(1) in a single operation.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
